<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Extrait d'Acte de Naissance - {{ demande.numeroDossier }}</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; color: #1e293b; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; }
        .frame { border: 4px double #1e3a8a; padding: 30px; position: relative; height: 92%; }
        .watermark { position: absolute; top: 40%; left: 15%; width: 70%; text-align: center; font-size: 48px; color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.4); transform: rotate(-45deg); font-weight: bold; z-index: -10; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 4px; }
        
        /* Header style */
        .republic-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .republic-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0; color: #1e3a8a; }
        .republic-motto { font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; margin: 2px 0 10px 0; }
        .divider { width: 120px; height: 1.5px; bg-color: #1e3a8a; background: #1e3a8a; margin: 5px auto; }
        
        .ministry { font-size: 10px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 5px; color: #64748b; }
        .commune { font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 2px; color: #0f172a; }
        
        /* Document Title */
        .doc-title { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0 25px 0; }
        .doc-title h1 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0; color: #1e3a8a; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .doc-title p { font-size: 11px; font-style: italic; color: #64748b; margin: 5px 0 0 0; }
        
        /* Details Table */
        .details-section { margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .info-row { margin-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px dotted #cbd5e1; padding-bottom: 4px; }
        .info-label { font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 11px; color: #475569; display: inline-block; width: 220px; }
        .info-value { font-size: 13px; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 500; }
        
        /* Footer/Signatures */
        .footer-signatures { margin-top: 50px; height: 160px; position: relative; }
        .qr-code-box { position: absolute; left: 10px; bottom: 10px; width: 100px; text-align: center; }
        .qr-image { width: 85px; height: 85px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 4px; border-radius: 6px; }
        .qr-text { font-size: 8px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 4px; font-family: sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; }
        
        .signature-box { position: absolute; right: 10px; bottom: 10px; width: 260px; text-align: center; }
        .sig-date { font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-style: italic; }
        .sig-title { font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #1e3a8a; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .sig-name { font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; text-decoration: underline; }
        
        .footer-note { text-align: center; font-size: 9px; color: #94a3b8; font-family: sans-serif; margin-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-top: 8px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="frame">
        <div class="watermark">Copie Certifiée</div>
        
        <div class="republic-header">
            <h2 class="republic-title">Répulique de Guinée</h2>
            <div class="republic-motto">Travail - Justice - Solidarité</div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <div class="ministry">Ministère de l'Administration du Territoire et de la Décentralisation</div>
            <div class="commune">Gouvernorat de Conakry - Commune de Kaloum</div>
            <div class="commune">Service de l'État Civil</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="doc-title">
            <h1>Extrait d'Acte de Naissance</h1>
            <p>N° Dossier : {{ demande.numeroDossier }} &bull; Acte Enregistré sous le N° : ACTE-{{ demande.id }}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="details-section">
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Nom de l'enfant :</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{ specific_data.nom|upper }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Prénom(s) de l'enfant :</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{ specific_data.prenom }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Sexe :</span>
                <span class="info-value">{% if specific_data.genre == 'M' %}Masculin (M){% else %}Féminin (F){% endif %}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Né(e) le :</span>
                <span class="info-value">{% if specific_data.date_naissance %}{{ specific_data.date_naissance|date("d/m/Y") }}{% else %}—{% endif %}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Lieu de naissance :</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{ specific_data.lieu_naissance }}</span>
            </div>
            
            <div style="margin: 20px 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #1e3a8a; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #1e3a8a; width: 120px;">Filiation</div>
            
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Prénom & Nom du Père :</span>
                <span class="info-value">{% if specific_data.prenom_pere %}{{ specific_data.prenom_pere }} {{ specific_data.nom_pere|upper }}{% else %}Non renseigné{% endif %}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Date de naissance du Père :</span>
                <span class="info-value">{% if specific_data.date_naissance_pere %}{{ specific_data.date_naissance_pere|date("d/m/Y") }}{% else %}Non renseigné{% endif %}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Profession du Père :</span>
                <span class="info-value">{% if specific_data.profession_pere %}{{ specific_data.profession_pere }}{% else %}Non renseigné{% endif %}</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-row" style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <span class="info-label">Prénom & Nom de la Mère :</span>
                <span class="info-value">{% if specific_data.prenom_mere %}{{ specific_data.prenom_mere }} {{ specific_data.nom_mere|upper }}{% else %}Non renseigné{% endif %}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Date de naissance de la Mère :</span>
                <span class="info-value">{% if specific_data.date_naissance_mere %}{{ specific_data.date_naissance_mere|date("d/m/Y") }}{% else %}Non renseigné{% endif %}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Profession de la Mère :</span>
                <span class="info-value">{% if specific_data.profession_mere %}{{ specific_data.profession_mere }}{% else %}Non renseigné{% endif %}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer-signatures">
            <div class="qr-code-box">
                <img class="qr-image" src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=150x150&data=https://mairie.gn/verify/{{ demande.uuid }}" alt="Verification QR Code" />
                <div class="qr-text">Vérification numérique</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="signature-box">
                <div class="sig-date">Fait à Kaloum, le {{ "now"|date("d/m/Y") }}</div>
                <div class="sig-title">L'Officier de l'État Civil de la Commune de Kaloum</div>
                <div class="sig-name">M. Diallo Ibrahima Sory</div>
                <div style="font-size: 10px; color: #64748b; margin-top: 2px;">Officier Délégué</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer-note">
            Cet extrait est délivré en conformité avec les registres de l'État Civil de la République de Guinée. 
            Toute altération ou falsification de ce document officiel s'expose à des poursuites judiciaires.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
